headline: T-Mobile Takes Friday Night 5G Lights to a Whole. New. Level: More Winners, More Ways to Win and $4M in Total Prizes Up for Grabs
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., July 17, 2025--T-Mobile (NASDAQ: TMUS) today announced the return of Friday Night 5G Lights, the game-changing competition turning high school football into a nationwide celebration of hometown pride.
